{"tid":1487634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Social Isolation 第一擊] 係條街度見到見到任何黑警，即屌！","createTime":"2019-08-19T10:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T11:09:21.000Z","uid":243928,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"11bc4602cd86ea27d1f807cd08a3fb68845e064d","tid":1487634,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:50:03.000Z","msg":"早兩日係條街度見到兩個行咇黑警，都幾後生，應該做左兩三年，我諗起爆眼少女，即刻當街當面屌柒佢地。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗問候老母，直接話佢地係黑社會、社會垃圾、違背良心、社會寄生蟲就得，屌到佢地頭耷耷、急急腳咁走。<br />\n<br />\n大家要養成良好習慣，時時刻刻提醒佢地的身分，佢地係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑社會、社會垃圾、違背良心、社會寄生蟲、過街老鼠</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d705c386d190a126319e55edfc3c3cff2522d197","tid":1487634,"uid":89994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:50:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7347991b0d258fe5ca5db28da47c070496d148cb","tid":1487634,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:50:37.000Z","msg":"黑社會"},{"pid":"b88ed73b673a1adbed322e64f1cafa6e02a4d466","tid":1487634,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:50:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cc0bc101d146f8c14d455ef2cfc944452b2b234","tid":1487634,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:51:01.000Z","msg":"正義之師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb7136be18299acddb0f04dc7c32a2e64c3b95b","tid":1487634,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:51:57.000Z","msg":"即使見到佢地執行緊職務都要屌，香港警民關係係完全破滅架喇"},{"pid":"24041ab1fe083223bb5408254be46a08e4cc17b9","tid":1487634,"uid":133873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"怕唔怕被佢截停抄id"},{"pid":"6d89678ac31abda1715e5ff538b1b54c5c2d6e46","tid":1487634,"uid":282490,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"11bc4602cd86ea27d1f807cd08a3fb68845e064d","tid":1487634,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:50:03.000Z","msg":"早兩日係條街度見到兩個行咇黑警，都幾後生，應該做左兩三年，我諗起爆眼少女，即刻當街當面屌柒佢地。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗問候老母，直接話佢地係黑社會、社會垃圾、違背良心、社會寄生蟲就得，屌到佢地頭耷耷、急急腳咁走。<br />\n<br />\n大家要養成良好習慣，時時刻刻提醒佢地的身分，佢地係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑社會、社會垃圾、違背良心、社會寄生蟲、過街老鼠</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:53:33.000Z","msg":"有人唔做<br />\n走去做狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打埋啲咁嘅工<br />\n預左無樽鹽架啦 <br />\n睥咩睥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分糧包埋比人鬧架<br />\n香港市民年年比差餉養你班垃圾<br />\n掉轉槍頭扑濕我地？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大搖大擺出黎行？<br />\n唔驚麻包袋咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c616a2b2cff36ac1518e0a235248b9826a63090","tid":1487634,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:54:23.000Z","msg":"好耐無係街見到狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 支持"},{"pid":"b20c0ef52ab90f7d578825173237f0fa09f990e8","tid":1487634,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T10:54:41.000Z","msg":"但都提醒大家，有幾個時刻屌之前要諗真<br />\n<br />\n1. 對方人多勢眾<br />\n<br />\n2. 對方多老野，呢班老屎忽點屌都唔會面紅<br />\n<br />\n3. 對方係藍帽子，分分鐘過黎打柒你<br />\n<br />\n緊記人多先好屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77455f8496a362c6cce4b5ccf62d14c79aa99db","tid":1487634,"uid":243928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24041ab1fe083223bb5408254be46a08e4cc17b9","tid":1487634,"uid":133873,"like":0,"di